<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 02:25:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>对于来自以色列基布兹的难民来说，人质的死亡再次唤醒了 10 月 7 日的创伤和愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/for-refugees-from-this-kibbutz-hostages-deaths-reawakens-the-trauma-and-anger-of-oct-7/0000018f-e4f5-d908-a9cf-edf79b810000</link><description>本周，饱受摧残的加沙边境基布兹尼尔奥兹社区遭受了自哈马斯近八个月前残暴袭击以来最严重的打击：官方确认其在加沙的人质已经死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 00:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/for-refugees-from-this-kibbutz-hostages-deaths-reawakens-the-trauma-and-anger-of-oct-7/0000018f-e4f5-d908-a9cf-edf79b810000</guid></item><item><title>AIPAC 任命埃利奥特·勃兰特 (Elliot Brandt) 为下一任首席执行官，接替长期担任首席执行官的霍华德·科尔 (Howard Kohr)</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/aipac-names-elliot-brandt-as-next-ceo-replacing-longtime-chief-howard-kohr/0000018f-e537-dce5-abdf-e73fec820000</link><description>勃兰特是这个强大的亲以色列组织的现任副首席执行官，他上任之际，AIPAC 正在瞄准被认为批评以色列的进步民主党人，并加强其对共和党初选的参与。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 21:55:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/aipac-names-elliot-brandt-as-next-ceo-replacing-longtime-chief-howard-kohr/0000018f-e537-dce5-abdf-e73fec820000</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院在拜登反对下通过国际刑事法院制裁法案，亲以色列民主党加入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-passes-icc-sanctions-bill-amid-biden-opposition-with-pro-israel-dems-joining/0000018f-e4f9-db2a-a5ff-e4fbf3720000</link><description>该法案是对国际刑事法院检察官卡里姆·汗向总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长加兰特发出逮捕令的回应</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 20:54:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-passes-icc-sanctions-bill-amid-biden-opposition-with-pro-israel-dems-joining/0000018f-e4f9-db2a-a5ff-e4fbf3720000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队希望加剧黎巴嫩战斗，担心公众不知道后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-wants-to-intensify-lebanon-fighting-fears-public-unaware-of-consequences/0000018f-e4d0-d1da-adaf-f5dfa6ff0000</link><description>以色列国防军负责人表示，以色列已准备好向黎巴嫩发动攻势，旨在让公众为更广泛的冲突做好准备。战时内阁周二晚上召开会议，与真主党讨论升级问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 20:27:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-wants-to-intensify-lebanon-fighting-fears-public-unaware-of-consequences/0000018f-e4d0-d1da-adaf-f5dfa6ff0000</guid></item><item><title>斯洛文尼亚在政府支持的议会投票后承认巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-04/ty-article/slovenia-recognizes-palestinian-state-after-parliamentary-vote-with-government-support/0000018f-e4de-d11f-a5cf-e7df5fce0000</link><description>上周，斯洛文尼亚政府批准了一项承认巴勒斯坦国的动议，并将其提交议会最终批准。总理加快了这一进程，以回应以色列最近对拉法的袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 20:16:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-04/ty-article/slovenia-recognizes-palestinian-state-after-parliamentary-vote-with-government-support/0000018f-e4de-d11f-a5cf-e7df5fce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学校长指责学生会在拟议法律中“麦卡锡主义煽动”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-university-heads-accuses-student-union-of-mccarthyist-incitement-in-proposed-law/0000018f-e4a6-d6de-a7df-f6ae29e20000</link><description>以色列的研究型大学反对学生会发起的一项法律，该法律“致命损害了学术独立和言论自由”，并要求学术机构解雇那些以被视为损害国家的方式发表言论的讲师</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 19:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-university-heads-accuses-student-union-of-mccarthyist-incitement-in-proposed-law/0000018f-e4a6-d6de-a7df-f6ae29e20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部燃烧，居民知道国家不会拯救他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-04/ty-article/.highlight/as-northern-israel-burns-residents-have-no-expectations-from-the-state/0000018f-e476-d6de-a7df-f67ec6fb0000</link><description>当真主党火箭弹袭击以色列北部社区时，勇敢的当地公民和志愿者迅速采取行动，不知疲倦地努力扑灭大火。与此同时，政府却无处可寻。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 18:36:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-04/ty-article/.highlight/as-northern-israel-burns-residents-have-no-expectations-from-the-state/0000018f-e476-d6de-a7df-f67ec6fb0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：泄露的文件显示，伊朗支付边缘反以色列新闻网站编辑的费用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-06-04/ty-article/report-fringe-anti-israel-news-site-editor-paid-by-iran-leaked-documents-show/0000018f-e389-dce5-abdf-e3adaf980000</link><description>《华盛顿邮报》的一篇报道透露，备受争议的在线媒体网站“灰色地带”的总编辑从伊朗一家国有新闻网络收取报酬。灰色地带被指控散布虚假信息并强烈支持伊朗、亲俄罗斯和反以色列的观点</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 18:07:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-06-04/ty-article/report-fringe-anti-israel-news-site-editor-paid-by-iran-leaked-documents-show/0000018f-e389-dce5-abdf-e3adaf980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 242 天：真主党表示不想扩大冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-242-hezbollah-says-it-does-not-want-to-expand-conflict/0000018f-e417-d1da-adaf-f59f16220001</link><description>卡塔尔表示已向哈马斯提交了以色列的停战建议 ■ 美国希望联合国安理会通过决议，支持拜登提出的停火协议 ■ 拜登告诉《时代》杂志，“有充分的理由”相信内塔尼亚胡出于政治考虑而延长战争■ 经过 20 小时与以色列北部的大火搏斗后，救援部门称他们重新控制了大部分火势 ■ 以下是战争开始 242 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:39:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-242-hezbollah-says-it-does-not-want-to-expand-conflict/0000018f-e417-d1da-adaf-f59f16220001</guid></item><item><title>世界中央厨房处于“高度戒备”状态，全面恢复在加沙的人道主义行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/on-very-high-alert-world-central-kitchen-fully-resumes-humanitarian-operations-in-gaza/0000018f-e3b6-d6de-a7df-f7be1dc00000</link><description>世界中央厨房在加沙设有 68 个正常运转的社区厨房，自以色列空袭导致 7 名志愿者死亡两个月后恢复活动以来，该厨房已提供了超过 350 万份餐食</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 15:56:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/on-very-high-alert-world-central-kitchen-fully-resumes-humanitarian-operations-in-gaza/0000018f-e3b6-d6de-a7df-f7be1dc00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将不会参加下一届威尼斯建筑双年展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-will-not-take-part-in-the-next-venice-architecture-biennale/0000018f-e2b6-d5cf-adcf-ffbe0cff0000</link><description>据以色列官员透露，以色列因展馆翻修，将不会在2025年举办展览。但正如一位艺术官员在加沙战争的背景下所说的那样，“现在当我们被排斥时，正是我们参与其中的时候”</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 15:23:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-will-not-take-part-in-the-next-venice-architecture-biennale/0000018f-e2b6-d5cf-adcf-ffbe0cff0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的破坏、饥饿和死亡是以色列的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/the-destruction-starvation-and-death-in-gaza-are-israels-defeat/0000018f-e31a-dce5-abdf-e33f1d9a0000</link><description>犹太国家之所以被击败，是因为它的政客和公职人员导致 230 万人挨饿受渴</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 14:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/the-destruction-starvation-and-death-in-gaza-are-israels-defeat/0000018f-e31a-dce5-abdf-e33f1d9a0000</guid></item><item><title>对于内塔尼亚胡来说，即使巴勒斯坦权力机构的阿巴斯对抗伊朗和哈马斯，他也不是合作伙伴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/to-netanyahu-abbas-pa-is-no-partner-even-when-he-stands-up-to-iran-and-hamas/0000018f-e2fb-d09a-afaf-fefb00c20000</link><description>阿巴斯在伊朗最高领导人的猛烈言论中表示，巴勒斯坦人不需要不必要的战争，并质疑哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的理由，但内塔尼亚胡仍然拒绝将巴勒斯坦权力机构视为另一个恐怖组织</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 13:59:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/to-netanyahu-abbas-pa-is-no-partner-even-when-he-stands-up-to-iran-and-hamas/0000018f-e2fb-d09a-afaf-fefb00c20000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的极端正统联盟伙伴在极右翼反对下支持以色列与哈马斯人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-ultra-orthodox-coalition-partners-back-hostage-deal-amid-far-right-opposition/0000018f-e343-d1da-adaf-f7cf0c8b0000</link><description>沙斯的支持是在前一天得到内塔尼亚胡的另一个极端正统派合作伙伴联合托拉犹太教的支持之后宣布的，他们支持任何释放人质的协议。斯莫特里奇和本·格维尔威胁要退出联盟</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 13:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-ultra-orthodox-coalition-partners-back-hostage-deal-amid-far-right-opposition/0000018f-e343-d1da-adaf-f7cf0c8b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部所有火势均已得到控制；真主党战斗加剧，数千英亩土地被烧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/firefighters-continue-to-battle-blazes-in-north-israel-thousands-of-acres-already-burned/0000018f-e26a-da42-a1ef-fafa7c140000</link><description>真主党火箭弹在以色列北部引发大火后，消防队正在努力限制其损害并控制其蔓延，这场大火已经烧毁了数千英亩的森林</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 11:16:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/firefighters-continue-to-battle-blazes-in-north-israel-thousands-of-acres-already-burned/0000018f-e26a-da42-a1ef-fafa7c140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战火，以色列人垂死挣扎，而内塔尼亚胡在国会为阿谀奉承者精心准备演讲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-in-flames-israelis-are-dying-netanyahus-only-plan-pick-a-tie-for-d-c-speech/0000018f-e299-df97-a78f-f2fb51db0000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的分析人士不断将宏伟计划归功于以色列总理。但没有计划——只有一个绝望、无能的领导人，操纵着一个曾经繁荣的国家，他根本不关心人质及其家人</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 11:13:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-in-flames-israelis-are-dying-netanyahus-only-plan-pick-a-tie-for-d-c-speech/0000018f-e299-df97-a78f-f2fb51db0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登正在敦促阿拉伯和穆斯林国家说服哈马斯接受人质释放协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/biden-enlisting-arab-muslim-countries-to-convince-hamas-to-accept-hostage-release-deal/0000018f-e257-db29-a3ef-ef5f8e060000</link><description>美国政府官员担心以色列总理内塔尼亚胡会利用哈马斯对该协议反应迟缓来破坏该协议，并正在加班加点地确保哈马斯感受到卡塔尔、土耳其和其他有影响力国家同意该协议的压力</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 09:12:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/biden-enlisting-arab-muslim-countries-to-convince-hamas-to-accept-hostage-release-deal/0000018f-e257-db29-a3ef-ef5f8e060000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡博士或比比先生：谁将决定加沙停火协议的命运？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/dr-netanyahu-or-mr-bibi-who-will-decide-israels-response-to-bidens-gaza-deal/0000018f-dfab-df97-a78f-fffbf1c90000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡保持所有选择的开放性，并成功地让所有试图预测他将走向何方的人感到困惑。 除了拜登的声明和利库德集团部长们相互矛盾的回应之外，公众别无选择，只能阅读14频道的字里行间。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/dr-netanyahu-or-mr-bibi-who-will-decide-israels-response-to-bidens-gaza-deal/0000018f-dfab-df97-a78f-fffbf1c90000</guid></item><item><title>战时内阁召开会议讨论真主党升级；以色列北部所有火势均已得到控制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article-live/biden-urges-get-it-done-as-u-s-seeks-international-backing-for-cease-fire-proposal/0000018f-e116-df75-a79f-e736e8c10000</link><description>以色列国防军司令：以色列“准备好”在黎巴嫩发动战争 ■ 以色列国防军：在加沙中部布赖吉营地开展行动的部队 ■ 世界中央厨房恢复加沙援助行动 ■ 消防员继续在以色列北部扑灭大火 ■ 以色列国防军：两名武装巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被杀计划枪击袭击 ■ 卡塔尔外交部表示正在等待以色列哈马斯对人质协议提案的明确回应 ■ 拜登就加沙停火提案：“这项协议必须完成”</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 02:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article-live/biden-urges-get-it-done-as-u-s-seeks-international-backing-for-cease-fire-proposal/0000018f-e116-df75-a79f-e736e8c10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院听取了针对禁止半岛电视台在以色列广播的法律的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-hears-petition-against-law-used-to-halt-al-jazeera-broadcasts-in-israel/0000018f-e0c6-df97-a78f-f2f723570000</link><description>法官团主席伊扎克·阿米特法官：毫无疑问，这里存在侵犯言论自由的行为</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 01:15:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-hears-petition-against-law-used-to-halt-al-jazeera-broadcasts-in-israel/0000018f-e0c6-df97-a78f-f2f723570000</guid></item></channel></rss>